The festival is particularly notable as featuring an appearance by John Lennon and Yoko Ono, as the Plastic Ono Band, with Eric Clapton, Klaus Voormann, bass player and designer of the Revolver album cover, and future Yes drummer Alan White. 
The appearance of John Lennon, Yoko Ono and The Plastic Ono Band was not publicly known in advance.
